# ![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,){.gb-icon .size-[1em] .text-tint-subtle .shrink-0}Welcome to Printr {#welcome-to-printr .text-4xl .font-bold .flex .items-center .gap-4 .grow .text-pretty .clear-right .xs:clear-none}

Glad to have you onboard ser!
::::

::::: {.grid .[&>*+*]:mt-5 .whitespace-pre-wrap}
**Printr** is the first **chain-abstracted** token launchpad where you
can **launch**, **trade,** and **discover tokens** across **70+
blockchains**[.]{.text-purple-500}..

There are many chains, and that\'s not a problem, as they all have their
specific strengths.

Tokenizing on a single chain is limiting and outdated. As a creator,
**you shouldn\'t** have to choose one to launch your tokens, your goal
should be able to reach to as many users and liquidity as possible.

Printr helps make that a reality. We're here to[
]{.text-yellow-600}**unite the trenches** and make memecoins truly
borderless.

**On Printr, you can:**

- :::: {.text-base .leading-normal .mr-1 .flex .min-h-lh .min-w-6 .items-center .justify-center .text-tint}
  ::: {.before:font-var .before:content-(--pseudoBefore--content) style="--pseudoBefore--content:'•';--font-family:Arial;font-size:min(1.5em, 24px);line-height:1"}
  :::
  ::::

  ::: {.flex .min-w-0 .flex-1 .flex-col .space-y-2}
  Launch your token on any chain or every chain.
  :::

- :::: {.text-base .leading-normal .mr-1 .flex .min-h-lh .min-w-6 .items-center .justify-center .text-tint}
  ::: {.before:font-var .before:content-(--pseudoBefore--content) style="--pseudoBefore--content:'•';--font-family:Arial;font-size:min(1.5em, 24px);line-height:1"}
  :::
  ::::

  ::: {.flex .min-w-0 .flex-1 .flex-col .space-y-2}
  Trade from anywhere into any chain.
  :::

- :::: {.text-base .leading-normal .mr-1 .flex .min-h-lh .min-w-6 .items-center .justify-center .text-tint}
  ::: {.before:font-var .before:content-(--pseudoBefore--content) style="--pseudoBefore--content:'•';--font-family:Arial;font-size:min(1.5em, 24px);line-height:1"}
  :::
  ::::

  ::: {.flex .min-w-0 .flex-1 .flex-col .space-y-2}
  Earn rewards!
  :::

Initially we\'ll be going live on **Solana, Base, BNB, Ethereum, Monad,
Avax, Mantle, and Arbitrum** - with **Sui coming soon.** Eventually, all
other chains will follow suit with cross-chain functionalities enabled.
